{"tid":2197080,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"試完Wireless Dex 覺得佢先係終極ARM PC","createTime":"2020-09-10T10:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:50:59.000Z","uid":131430,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"191ecba0e288f9fdfe30ee737465ed94df3efeca","tid":2197080,"uid":131430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"Apple Silicon Mac有個好大問題我一直諗唔通<br />\n佢最大賣點係用到Apps 同功效好<br />\n點解iphone ipad mac 用同一粒u 唔可以合埋做1-2 部<br />\n<br />\n今日試左Samsung 無線連moon, keyboard, mouse 可以完全當獨立電腦用<br />\nInput Delay 絕對可以接受範圍<br />\n講到呢到 我知你想屌咩 Android OS 同電腦比on9丫嘛？<br />\n但當Apple可以行ARM MAC OS 點解 Android 唔可以行Windows OS?<br />\n只要過幾年ARM夠勁 或者有人解決到dual OS問題<br />\n電腦已經非必要 只須要一個moon, 要拎出街就portable moon<br />\n一個moon 比盡$3000 一部portable laptop $8000起跳<br />\n<br />\n結論係根本Apple有能力做到二合一  佢係唔做 <br />\nSteve Jobs 同 Tim Cook 最大分別就係唔夠革新<br />\n而Samsung係慢慢行緊呢條路 二合為一"},{"pid":"f8fccfbb6f4fbc59a18ed984015a906ec4933e25","tid":2197080,"uid":5159,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"無錯係做到,<br />\n但無人鐘意做工程師"},{"pid":"2604d6059b1b03561c88fc40e238d7080cdaa350","tid":2197080,"uid":131430,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f8fccfbb6f4fbc59a18ed984015a906ec4933e25","tid":2197080,"uid":5159,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"無錯係做到,<br />\n但無人鐘意做工程師"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"係無人鍾意收三份錢變成收一份<br />\n因為ipad 同mac都變得多餘"},{"pid":"63b71097c7277db65fb83d730d8689c749fdac71","tid":2197080,"uid":19789,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2604d6059b1b03561c88fc40e238d7080cdaa350","tid":2197080,"uid":131430,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f8fccfbb6f4fbc59a18ed984015a906ec4933e25","tid":2197080,"uid":5159,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"無錯係做到,<br />\n但無人鐘意做工程師"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"係無人鍾意收三份錢變成收一份<